SubjectP.C. 2017-60 of January 25, 2017 ** AMENDMENT **
PrecisOrder amending Order in Council P.C. 2017-60 of January 25, 2017 by replacing the words “Parliamentary Secretary to the Minister of Indigenous and Northern Affairs” with the words “Parliamentary Secretary to the Minister of Crown-Indigenous Relations and Northern Affairs and the Minister of Indigenous Services”.
